notes.text:
This update for webkit2gtk3 fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2022-32893: Fixed several crashes and rendering issues (bsc#1202807).

- Fixed WebKitGTK not allow to be used from non-main threads (bsc#1202169).

notes.text: An out-of-bounds write issue was addressed with improved bounds checking. This issue is fixed in iOS 15.6.1 and iPadOS 15.6.1, macOS Monterey 12.5.1, Safari 15.6.1. Processing maliciously crafted web content may lead to arbitrary code execution. Apple is aware of a report that this issue may have been actively exploited.
